result.name: 陸記正宗桂林米粉

reviews.text: 30 Jan 19: I used to have dinner here, there has variety of choices and food quality is very stable, the soup without any artificial ingredient (they claimed), place is clean but crowd. I love the Double-pork rice noodles which has BBQ pork neck and roasted pork, it is delicious 😋 you won’t feel the pork is oily and fatty, peanuts and vegetables are balancing the taste of the noodles. Drinks are good (even not the best in town).
Sadly, remain one in Yuen Long Yau San St.  If you like spicy noodle, I highly recommend you to dine here.  The drink at tea time is included.
Noodle are fine, but the environment will make u want to leave

So this is my go-to place whenever I feel like something spicy.

Set meal is inexpensive that includes spicy noodles and drink or a dessert.
Staff are very friendly, food is good. Cloudy, not very comfortable

reviews.text: 這次吃燒肉不夠脆口，有點太硬，平時吃是不錯的。在元朗來說性價比不算高！

30 Jan 19: I used to have dinner here, there has variety of choices and food quality is very stable, the soup without any artificial ingredient (they claimed), place is clean but crowd. I love the Double-pork rice noodles which has BBQ pork neck and roasted pork, it is delicious 😋 you won’t feel the pork is oily and fatty, peanuts and vegetables are balancing the taste of the noodles. Drinks are good (even not the best in town).
早10幾年前興過既桂林米粉，而家又有幾多地方有得食呢？
雙豬飯 加辣椒真係好好味
10多年後再吃，懷念的味道。
